{"ts":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"jf-644n"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Replace YAML-like output with official TOON serialization"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"The default output path is labeled TOON but uses a bespoke YAML-like envelope rather than the official Token-Oriented Object Notation implementation requested by the project contract. Adopt the current official @toon-format/toon encoder, preserve typed envelopes and redaction, validate lossless decode/schema behavior, and update every user/agent document and compatibility test."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":0},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agents","format","output","serialization","toon"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/assignee","value":"codex-jellyfin"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-jellyfin"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":360},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"All toon output is encoded with the latest compatible official @toon-format/toon package; Every emitted document round-trips through the official decoder to the exact JSON data model; Redaction and typed envelope semantics remain intact across all formatter helpers; README and docs distinguish TOON from YAML and show valid current syntax; Bun and npm lockfiles are reproducible and audited; Actual jf-cli read-only live commands validate TOON output without persisting private data"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/definition_of_ready","value":"Official package API and types verified from installed node_modules; duplicate-safe PM search completed; live server read-only mode available."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/goal","value":"jf-mqpo"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/value","value":"Make the default agent format genuinely compact, interoperable, and standards-based."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/impact","value":"Corrects the central LLM-facing output contract across every command without altering Jellyfin data."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/outcome","value":"Official TOON v4 serialization is the default validated output for all CLI commands."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/why_now","value":"The current default contradicts the explicit project requirement and blocks trustworthy agent/programmatic workflows."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"jf-gn5j"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/sprint","value":"jellyfin-10.11.11"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/reporter","value":"codex-jellyfin"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Run jf-cli --format toon on a uniform list; observe YAML list syntax without TOON array counts or field headers. Compare with @toon-format/toon encode output and official specification fixtures."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"Default and explicit toon output is standards-conformant TOON generated by the official package and losslessly decodes to the intended typed envelope."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"The formatter manually emits YAML-like text and documentation calls TOON YAML, so external TOON decoders cannot rely on the output contract."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/affected_version","value":"2026.7.21-3"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/component","value":"formatters"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/regression","value":false},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/customer_impact","value":"Agents lose the token-efficiency, schema guardrails, and interoperable validation promised by the default format; programmatic consumers can mistake YAML for TOON."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"jf-59hr","kind":"related_to","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin"},{"id":"jf-lpki","kind":"related_to","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin"},{"id":"jf-mkzh","kind":"related_to","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin"},{"id":"jf-sylm","kind":"related_to","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin"},{"id":"jf-w5ow","kind":"related_to","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Official sources reviewed on 2026-07-23: toon-format/toon is the reference TypeScript implementation and @toon-format/toon 4.0.0 is the current npm release; the published spec describes lossless JSON-model encoding with explicit array lengths and tabular headers."}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-23T04:53:59.365Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Do not replace TOON with YAML aliases or a home-grown encoder. Use top-level imports from the installed official package and inspect its bundled type declarations before implementation."}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/files","value":[{"path":"src/formatters/base.ts","scope":"project","note":"Current bespoke envelope serializer"},{"path":"src/formatters/toon.ts","scope":"project","note":"Public TOON formatter facade"},{"path":"src/formatters/index.ts","scope":"project","note":"Cross-format dispatcher"},{"path":"package.json","scope":"project","note":"Official encoder dependency and release gates"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tests","value":[{"command":"bun test tests/formatters/toon.test.ts tests/formatters/base.test.ts tests/formatters/formatters-coverage.test.ts","path":"package.json","scope":"project","