{"ts":"2026-07-23T05:08:43.853Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-23T05:08:43.852Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Implemented official @toon-format/toon 4.0.0 encoding/decoding, normalized canonical formatter type names and descriptive fields to the JSON Schema registry, fixed error/read-only bypass output, added direct decode-to-schema contract coverage, refreshed agent/TOON docs, and advanced the release tooling pin to pm CLI 2026.7.22. Unit suite: 915 pass, 177 live skips, 0 fail; typecheck/lint/file-length pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-23T05:08:43.853Z"}],"before_hash":"c15c9110a080768f22db003a4bf05f9aed2dbb62a17ba572df9656a1be807781","after_hash":"a6927bbdc4f1930b714bc4b9128533458ebe20543941edfcfff42ef9d741cf4d"}
{"ts":"2026-07-23T05:08:44.745Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-23T05:08:44.744Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Design decision: TOON is now a distinct standards-backed wire format. YAML remains separately supported; schema auto-detection tries JSON, strict TOON, then YAML. Empty arrays, nulls, and false values are preserved because removing them changes output semantics and breaks schema contracts."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-23T05:08:44.745Z"}],"before_hash":"a6927bbdc4f1930b714bc4b9128533458ebe20543941edfcfff42ef9d741cf4d","after_hash":"d722095e01f6128adc58e26fcd8155571e67217dbd5092baebcb94bef42859fd"}
